import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    scatter = ax.scatter(data['x'], data['y'], c=data['color'], label=data['name'])
    ax.set_xlabel('x')
    ax.set_ylabel('y')
    plt.title('What is the correlation between x and y?', wrap=True)
    legend1 = ax.legend(*scatter.legend_elements(), title="Names")
    ax.add_artist(legend1)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['lumosity'], bins=30, color='blue', alpha=0.7, label='Lumosity')
    plt.xlabel('Lumosity')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of lumosity?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['saturation'].plot.hist(bins=20, alpha=0.7, color='blue', edgecolor='black')
    plt.axvline(data['saturation'].median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f"Median: {data['saturation'].median():.2f}")
    plt.xlabel('Saturation')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of saturation?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    color_counts = data['color'].value_counts()
    color_counts.plot(kind='bar', color=color_counts.index)
    plt.xlabel('Color')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of color?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend(color_counts.index, title='Colors', bbox_to_anchor=(1.05, 1), loc='upper left')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    key_counts = data['key'].value_counts()
    keys = key_counts.index
    frequencies = key_counts.values

    plt.bar(keys, frequencies)
    plt.xlabel('Key')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of key?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend(['Key Frequencies'])

    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
